data.description: Price adjustment just made, so don't miss this opportunity! This split floor plan, 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom house has ample room for all your needs. As you step inside, you will be greeted through the foyer to an open and inviting living space with large windows allowing plenty of natural light to come through. The kitchen is open to the living room and dining room for a great entertainment space with a large eat-in island and walk-in pantry. A standout feature of this home is the screened-in back porch. It's a perfect retreat to enjoy the outdoors while being protected from the mosquitos, and provides a comfortable and cozy space to relax.  The oversized master bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom complete with extra storage shelves and a humongous closet. This well-designed home combines functionality and style for an ideal living space for you! As a bonus, this wonderful house includes a storage shed in the privacy-fenced backyard adding extra space for storing gardening tools, outdoor equipment, or anything else to keep you organized. All this, and it is in flood zone X (which is good). Call your Realtor today! All measurements are more/less.
